      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FAIRWAY TO HEAVEN (5) classy filly who returns from a let-up. Showed an explosive turn of foot on resumption with a dominant Maiden victory over 1000m at Kembla Grange. Ticks plenty of boxes and will take catching over this trip. SOMERTON SMART (2) returned from a lengthy break with a courageous fourth over this trip at Scone in C2 grade. Comes to hand quickly and no shock to see him a little closer to the speed. Top-three player. LIGHTHOUSE LASS (7) good filly who comes here in peak condition fourth-up. Faded late in the soft (7) conditions when second over 1150m at Randwick Kensington in BM72 class. Back in grade and shapes as one of the leading chances. STUBBORN EMMELIE (9) bounced off her good debut second with a fighting Maiden win over 1000m at Gosford. Heading in the right direction and looks up to this tougher contest.",
